"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The idea of protracted war is the left-handed criticism of the speculism of quick victory, and the right-handed criticism of Xiong's surrenderism.\\n\\nThe speculative theory of quick victory believes that the end of 2021 will be as precise as 2017, allowing the leeks to escape successfully before the Qing retreat on December 31.\\n\\nThe capitulationism of bear theory believes that the double top bull market has been completed in 2021, and 65,000 is the big top of this round of bull market. The next three years will be a long bear.\\n\\nThe limited experience given to us by traditional economic laws is that a sufficiently powerful intervention can distort the cycle, but it is not enough to eliminate it. It's like the kind of effect our powerful legal currency system has done for the intervention of the capitalist economic crisis cycle.\",\"timestamp\":1634474980,\"title\":\"Leveraged shorts are the friend of spot longs, and leveraged longs are the enemy of spot longs.\"},\"digest\":\"Pc3jE1CKPIwHvnF2wzmDKUI37yOz51nOdlocRLxEdyc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x786A462440284ea9231f3A988Fc9404A28C9dA45\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N5aMT2_USLbw-Wn_ER8tkfk0Hi2DxIHscPJ10hdTHlM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vVyLXUJ8gz4oCqKAI4RJJzxp-ak1mnCpMGJrJbX5Y0E\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"7kJqYXvf42PEqzjhHka0qc3Ci4x3bl1HH14Cz087clKnyyKZdKdZJoUJPdbJ34Qv7Lf7zzixFebjWgBfu6V_SQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x62cb12b477ba868ff5641b2dd3792ca8b599f42cad6f9a7921d129d80c46fa411f81214fd0e262fa9f14e9d69ba9d0ede681ad058716ab6828d2ca963ca0ded31b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N5aMT2_USLbw-Wn_ER8tkfk0Hi2DxIHscPJ10hdTHlM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vVyLXUJ8gz4oCqKAI4RJJzxp-ak1mnCpMGJrJbX5Y0E\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\